---
title: SuperQuick Cheesy Sausage Flatbreads with Pesto and Spinach Salad
description: This recipe might be speedy and easy, but there's nothing simple about the flavours! Flatbreads are the perfect base for savoury pesto and Italian sausage, while a fresh spinach-and-tomato side salad cuts through the richness to tick all the boxes.

